    "This deviation becomes more pronounced as either δ and/or N increases.",
    "It is clear that the derived optimal bit detection threshold γ opt provides a significant BEP improvement compared to the suboptimal detection threshold γ subopt, particularly for higher values of δ, as shown in Fig. 2(b).",
